Technical Specifications for Image Creation:

Base Properties:
- Dimensions: 256x256 pixels
- Format: PNG (optimized lossless compression)
- Color Profile: sRGB
- Transparency: Enabled
- Target File Size: < 10KB
- Metadata: Stripped

Design Elements:
1. Background:
   - 8px grid pattern lines
   - Light theme: #E5E7EB with 15% opacity
   - Dark theme: #374151 with 15% opacity

2. Icon:
   - Centered position
   - 64x64px dimensions
   - Minimal outline style
   - Purpose: Visual placeholder indicator

3. Border:
   - Width: 1px
   - Style: Solid
   - Light theme: #D1D5DB
   - Dark theme: #4B5563

Responsive Variants:
- 128x128px (0.5x)
- 256x256px (1x)
- 512x512px (2x)

Performance Optimizations:
- Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
- CDN Distribution: Enabled
- Browser Caching: Enabled
- Loading: lazy
- Preload Priority: low

Accessibility Requirements:
- Alt text required (non-decorative)
- Minimum contrast ratio: 4.5:1
- Target contrast ratio: 7:1
- ARIA role: img
- Screen reader compatible

Usage Contexts:
- Loading states
- Empty states
- Failed image loads
- Default profile images
- Content placeholders
- Skeleton screens